# {{name}}

A research agent powered by Claude and Castari. This agent can search the web, read web pages, and synthesize findings into comprehensive reports.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Deploy to Castari
cast deploy

# Invoke the agent
cast invoke {{name}} "Research the current state of AI agents in 2026"
```

## Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run locally (reads prompt from stdin)
echo "Research the benefits of TypeScript" | npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build
```

## Example Research Prompts

```bash
# Technology research
echo "Compare the top 3 cloud providers for serverless computing" | npm run dev

# Market research
echo "What are the latest trends in AI development?" | npm run dev

# Technical comparison
echo "Compare React vs Vue vs Svelte for building web apps" | npm run dev

# Save a report
